Package: termuxfetch
Version: 2.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: bash
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Neofetch‑like system information tool for Termux
 termuxfetch displays a colourful ASCII art banner along with
 essential system information: Android version, Termux version,
 kernel, device model, uptime, package count, CPU, memory, shell,
 and architecture – all in a compact terminal output.
